    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1926-07-20T03:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1926-07-20T03:00:00-05:00" n="635"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d635">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">883.6363/15: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Egypt</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Alexandria</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1926-07-20T10:00:00+02:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 20, 1926—10 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received July 20—9:17 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>28. Your telegram No. 17, July 19, 5 p.m. Had conferred with representative of
                    company several times. Shall press further for a reply from Government to
                    written and oral representations made by Legation June 8th, 29th, July 10th.
                    Report by mail.<note n="20" xml:id="d635fn20">See <hi rend="italic">infra.</hi>
                    </note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Johnson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
